flowchart TD
    %% Nodes
    Start([Start: Dev Pulls Tag from Master])
    Branch[Create Feature/Fix Branch]
    Work[Code, Commit, Push]
    CI{CI Pipeline\nTests & Coverage}
    FixCI[Fix Issues]
    PR[Create Pull Request]
    
    %% Logic Gates
    IsReg[Is QA Regression Active?]
    IsFix[Is this a Regression Fix?]
    
    %% Paths
    DevDeploy[Deploy to DEV from Branch]
    ReviewStandard[Standard Code Review]
    ReviewStrict[Strict Review:\n2 Approvers + Owner]
    Merge[Merge to Master]
    
    %% Deployment
    ProdDeploy[Deploy to PROD from Master]
    Tag[Create Tag: YYYY_MMM_ReleaseName]
    Unlock[Unlock Master Branch]
    
    %% Graph Connections
    Start --> Branch
    Branch --> Work
    Work --> CI
    CI -- Fail --> FixCI
    FixCI --> Work
    CI -- Pass --> PR
    
    PR --> IsReg
    
    %% Regression/Lock Logic
    IsReg -- YES (Master Locked) --> IsFix
    
    IsFix -- NO (New Feature/POC) --> DevDeploy
    DevDeploy --> Wait[Wait for Lock to End]
    
    IsFix -- YES --> ReviewStrict
    ReviewStrict --> Merge
    
    %% Normal Flow
    IsReg -- NO (Normal Dev) --> ReviewStandard
    ReviewStandard --> Merge
    
    %% Release Flow
    Merge --> ProdDeploy
    ProdDeploy --> Tag
    Tag --> Unlock
    
    %% Styling
    style IsReg fill:#ff9999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Tag fill:#99ff99,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DevDeploy fill:#ffff99,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
